		<h1 class="uk-article-title">
					Paid internship in China: Business Developer in Investment Banking			</h1>
	
	

		<p class="uk-article-meta">

		
	</p>
	

	
		<div>
		
<p>Investment bank that advices reputable US and European multinationals to make strategic investments in Asia through mergers and acquisitions and joint ventures or, to divest business/assets.</p>
 
<p>This investment bank focusing on M&amp;A, restructuring, and capital raising has been consistently owned and managed by the same team over 8 years. It has offices in strategic cities such as New York, London, Seoul, Hong Kong, Beijing, Shanghai, Tokyo, Mumbai and Bahrain.</p>
<p>Location: <strong>Shanghai &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong> <br />Field:<strong> Business Development&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />Length: <strong>3- 6 months</strong><br />Industry: <strong>Investment banking&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />Level: <strong>Intern &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><br />Start Date: <strong>January</strong></p>
<p>Requirements:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fluent in English and Good English writing skills is a must;</li>
<li>Intern experience gained at foreign invested investment banks, private equity funds, and securities companies (equity research).&nbsp; Experience at consulting and market research firms is also relevant. &nbsp;</li>
<li>Highly motivated, strong integrity and keen to take initiatives, work effectively both independently and with other team members, has good communication and computer skills</li>
<li>Minimum 3 days a week in 3 months. Full time internship is a plus<br />Responsibilities:</li>
<li>Support execution of corporate finance transactions, including business analysis, valuation, due diligence, documentation;</li>
<li>Support marketing activities and prepare presentation materials for local and overseas offices</li>
<li>Conduct industry and company research, including substantial desktop research, telephone interviews and visits;</li>
<li>Attend meetings and assist in presenting materials to clients in English;</li>
<li>Conduct detailed search for investment candidates based on the client's specified criteria;</li>
<li>Other supporting work requested, e.g. translation, documentation.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;<br />Benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Remuneration from 2500</li>
</ul>	</div>
	
	
	
	


